cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use KNOTstore, please cite it as below."
title: "KNOTstore (LENS-64S): Knot-Addressed Structural Hashing and Tiny-Pointer Storage"
abstract: >-
  A content-addressed storage engine with O(1) address-regenerating retrieval,
  1-byte tiny pointers, SimHash near-duplicate locality, Merkle tamper-evidence,
  and reversible rollback provenance — plus a suite of downloadable applications
  (KnotVault, PrefixForge, DriftLedger, CheckpointTime).
type: software
authors:
  - name: "lumenhelixsolutions"
version: "0.2.0"
date-released: "2026-06-30"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/lumenhelixsolutions/KNOTstore"
url: "https://lumenhelixsolutions.github.io/KNOTstore/"
keywords:
  - content-addressed storage
  - deduplication
  - simhash
  - merkle
  - provenance
  - LLM prefix cache
